quran[111]{c,v,t}:
  17,1,Ulemerero ukhale kwa Iye amene adayendetsa kapolo wake nthawi ya usiku kuchoka ku Mzikiti Wolemekezeka kupita ku Mzikiti wakutali umene malo ake ozungulira tidawadalitsa; kuti timuonetse zina za zizindikiro zathu. Ndithudi Iye ndiwakumva ndipo woona zonse
  17,2,"Ndipo Ife tidamupatsa Mose Buku ndipo tidalipanga ilo kukhala chilangizo cha ana a Israyeli ponena kuti, “Musasankhe wina aliyense kupatula Ine kukhala wokutetezani.”"
  17,3,oh inu ana a iwo amene tidawanyamula pamodzi ndi Nowa! Ndithudi Iye adali kapolo wothokoza kwambiri
  17,4,"Ife tidavumbulutsa kwa ana a Israyeli, m’Buku kuti, mosakayika, inu mudzabweretsa chisokonezo padziko kachiwiri ndipo mudzakhala ankhanza ndi odzikweza kwambiri"
  17,5,"Ndipo litadza pangano loyamba, Ife tidzakutumizirani akapolo athu a gulu la nkhondo ankhongono zedi. Iwo amalowa m’katikati mwa nyumba zanu. Ndipo linali lonjezo limene linakwaniritsidwa"
  17,6,Titatero tidakupatsani mphamvu powagonjetsa iwo. Ndipo tidakuonjezerani chuma ndi ana ndipo tidakupangani kukhala anthu ambiri amphamvu
  17,7,"Ngati inu muchita zabwino, mukudzichitira nokha ubwinowo, koma ngati muchita zoipa, mukudzichitiranso nokha. Ndipo pamene pangano lomaliza lidza, Ife tidzalola adani anu kuti akumvetseni chisoni ndi kulowa mu Mzikiti wanu monga momwe adaloweramo koyamba ndi kukantha kwenikweni onse amene adawapeza"
  17,8,"Mwina Ambuye wanu adzakuchitirani chifundo koma ngati inu mubwerera kuuchimo, nafenso tidzabwezera kukanthani. Ife takonza Gahena kukhala ndende ya anthu osakhulupirira"
  17,9,"Ndithudi Korani ino imatsogolera ku zinthu zabwino ndipo imawauza anthu okhulupirira, amene amachita zabwino, kuti adzakhala ndi malipiro aakulu"
  17,10,Ndipo iwo amene sakhulupirira za tsiku lotsiriza Ife tawakonzera chilango chowawa
  17,11,Ndipo munthu amapempha zoipa monga momwe amapemphera zabwino ndipo munthu ndi wopupuluma
  17,12,"Ndipo tidapanga usiku ndi usana kukhala zizindikiro zathu ziwiri. Ndipo tidakuta chizindikiro chausiku ndi mdima pamene tidaika chizindikiro chamasana kukhala chooneka kuti inu muzifunafuna zabwino zochokera kwa Ambuye wanu, komanso kuti mudziwe kuchuluka kwa zaka ndi chiwerengero. Ndipo zinthu zonse tazifotokoza momveka"
  17,13,Ndipo Ife tidamangirira ntchito za munthu aliyense pakhosi lake ndipo patsiku lachiweruzo tidzamutulutsira buku limene adzalipeze lili lotsekulidwa
  17,14,werenga Buku lako. Lero pakwana kuti mzimu wako udziwerengere wokha zonse zimene unkachita
  17,15,"Aliyense amene achita zabwino atero podzipulumutsa yekha. Ndipo aliyense amene achita zoipa, atero podzipweteka yekha. Palibe amene adzanyamula katundu wa mnzake. Ndipo Ife sitilanga pokhapokha ngati tatumiza Mtumwi"
  17,16,"Ndipo pamene Ife tifuna kuononga Mzinda, poyamba timatumiza ulamuliro wathu kwa anthu ake opeza bwino. Ndipo iwo amauphwanya, ndipo motero liwu la chilango limatsimikiza pa iwo. Ndipo Ife timauononga kwambiri"
  17,17,Kodi ndi mibadwo ingati ya anthu imene taononga pambuyo pa Nowa? Ambuye wako wakwana kukhala Wozindikira ndi woona zolakwa za akapolo ake
  17,18,"Aliyense amene afuna chisangalalo cha msanga Ife timapereka msanga chimene Ife tifuna kwa amene Ife tamufuna. Ndipo pambuyo pake tamukonzera iye Gahena, imene adzalowa monyozedwa ndi mokankhidwa"
  17,19,"Ndipo yense amene afuna moyo umene uli nkudza, ndi kumaugwirira ntchito zake molimbika, ndipo ndi wokhulupirira, amenewo ndi amene ntchito zawo zidzakhala zoyamikidwa"
  17,20,Ife timapereka kuchokera ku mphatso za Ambuye wako. Ndipo mphatso za Ambuye wako sizokanizidwa kwa aliyense
  17,21,"Taona mmene tawalemekezera ena kuposa anzawo ndipo, ndithudi, moyo umene uli nkudza uli ndi ulemu wambiri ndipo ndi waukulu poyerekeza"
  17,22,Musasankhe mulungu wina ndi kumuphatikiza ndi Mulungu weniweni chifukwa mungadzakhale ndi manyazi ndi wopanda wokuthandizani
  17,23,"Ndipo Ambuye wako walamula kuti musapembedze wina aliyense koma Iye yekha. Ndipo kuti muwachitire makolo anu zabwino. Ngati wina wa iwo kapena onse akalamba ali kukhala nanu, musawakalipire ayi, koma muziwayankhula ndi mawu aulemu"
  17,24,"Onetsani kudzichepetsa ndi chisoni ndipo munene kuti, “Ambuye wanga! Achitireni chifundo monga momwe iwo adandilerera pamene ine ndidali wamng’ono.”"
  17,25,Ambuye wanu amadziwa kwambiri zonse zimene zili m’mitima mwanu. Ngati muli abwino ndithudi Iye ali wokhululukira kwa anthu amene amadza kwa Iye nthawi zonse modzichepetsa ndi kulapa
  17,26,Ndipo apatseni abale anu ndi anthu ovutika gawo lawo lowayenera ndiponso a paulendo amene avutika. Ndipo musapereke chuma chanu moononga
  17,27,"Ndithudi anthu oononga ndi abale a Satana ndipo Satana, kwa Ambuye wake, ndi wosayamika"
  17,28,"Ndipo ngati iwe siuwathandiza ndipo uli kuyembekezera chisomo chochokera kwa Ambuye wako, yankhula nawo mwachifundo ndi mawu oleza"
  17,29,Ndipo musakhale oumira kapena opereka moononga chifukwa mungadzudzulidwe kapena kukhala osauka kwambiri
  17,30,"Ndithudi Ambuye wako amapereka zambiri kwa aliyense amene wamufuna ndipo amanyalapsa. Ndithudi Iye, kwa akapolo ake, ndi wodziwa ndi woona"
  17,31,Ndipo musawaphe ana anu chifukwa choopa umphawi. Ife timawapatsa zosowa zawo ndi inu nomwe. Ndithudi kuwapha iwo ndi tchimo lalikulu
  17,32,Ndipo musayandikire chigololo. Ndithudi icho ndi chonyansa ndiponso njira yoipa
  17,33,"Ndipo musaphe wina aliyense amene Mulungu waletsa pokhapokha ngati pali chifukwa chololedwa. Ndipo aliyense amene waphedwa mopanda chilungamo, Ife tamupatsa m’bale wake mphamvu zobwezera kapena kukhululuka pa imfa yake. Koma m’bale wakeyo asapyole muyeso pa kubwezeraku. Ndithudi iye ndi wotetezedwa"
  17,34,Ndipo musachiyandikire chuma cha mwana wamasiye kupatula ngati muli ndi cholinga chochisamala mpaka pamene mwini wake adzafike pa msinkhu woti akhoza kuchisamalira yekha. Ndipo kwaniritsani lonjezo lililonse. Ndithudi! mudzafunsidwa za lonjezoli
  17,35,Ndipo kwaniritsani muyeso pamene muyesa zinthu ndipo yesani mwachilungamo polinga zinthu pa sikelo. Zimenezo ndizo zabwino ndipo ndi mapeto abwino kwambiri
  17,36,Ndipo musatsatire zinthu zimene simuzidziwa. Ndithudi kumvera kapena kuyang’ana kapenanso kuganizira kwa mumtima mwa munthu kudzafufuzidwa pa tsiku lachiweruzo
  17,37,"Ndipo musayende modzitukumula pa dziko lapansi, ndithudi, inu simungathe kuboola nthaka ndi kufika kutalika kwa mapiri"
  17,38,Kuipa kwa zonsezi sikukondweretsa Ambuye wako
  17,39,"Ili ndi gawo la luntha limene Ambuye wako wakuuza iwe. Ndipo usatumikire mulungu wina kuonjezera pa Mulungu weniweni chifukwa mwina iwe ungaponyedwe ku Gahena, modzudzulidwa ndi mokankhidwa"
  17,40,Kodi Ambuye wanu wakusankhirani inu ana aamuna ndipo wadzisankhira Iye mwini ana aakazi kuchokera kwa Angelo? Ndithudi! Inu mukuyankhula mawu oopsa
  17,41,"Ndithudi Ife tafotokoza chinthu chilichonse m’Korani iyi kuti iwo achenjezedwe, koma iyo siili kuonjezera chilichonse koma kuipidwa"
  17,42,"Nena, “Kukadakhala kuti kuli milungu ina yoonjezera pa Mulungu weniweni, monga momwe akunenera, iyo ikadapeza njira yoti ikhale pafupi ndi Mulungu.”"
  17,43,"Kuyamikidwa ndi kukhala pamwamba, kukhale kwake! Kuchokera ku bodza lalikulu limene iwo ali nkunena"
  17,44,"Miyamba isanu ndi iwiri, dziko lapansi ndi zonse zimene zimakhala m’menemo zimamulemekeza Iye ndipo palibe chinthu chomwe sichimulemekeza Mulungu. Koma inu simumva mayamiko. Ndithudi Iye ndi woleza mtima ndipo ndi wokhululukira nthawi zonse"
  17,45,"Pamene iwe umawerenga Korani, Ife timaika, pakati pa iwe ndi iwo amene sakhulupirira za moyo umene uli nkudza tchingo losaoneka"
  17,46,Ndipo Ife taika zophimba m’mitima mwawo kuti mwina angaizindikire ndi m’makutu mwawo kuti asaimvetse. Ndipo pamene iwe utchula Ambuye wako yekha mu Korani iwo amatembenuka kuthawa mosangalala
  17,47,"Ife timadziwa kwambiri zimene iwo akumva ndi pamene amamvetsera kwa iwe. Ndipo pamene amanong’onezana, taona anthu oipa, amanena kuti: “Inu mukutsatira munthu wolodzedwa.”"
  17,48,Taona mmene akuperekera zitsanzo zokhudza iwe. Motero iwo asochera ndipo sangathe kupeza njira
  17,49,"Ndipo iwo amati, “Kodi pamene ife tidzasanduka mafupa ndi zidutswa zopereseka kodi tidzaukitsidwanso kukhala chilengedwe chatsopano?”"
  17,50,"Nena, “Khalani miyala kapena zitsulo.”"
  17,51,"“Kapena cholengedwa china chimene ndi chachikulu m’mitima mwanu.” Iwo adzati, “Ndani amene adzatibwezeranso?” Nena, “Iye amene adakulengani poyamba.” Ndipo iwo adzapukusa mitu yawo ndipo kwa iwe adzafunsa kuti, “Kodi zimenezi zidzachitika liti?” Nena, “Mwina zili pafupi.”"
  17,52,"Pa tsiku limene Iye adzakuitanani ndipo inu mudzamuyankha ndi matamando ake ndi kumvera, pamenepo inu mudzaganiza kuti simudakhale nthawi yaitali koma yochepa"
  17,53,"Auze akapolo anga kuti aziyankhula zokhazo zimene zili zabwino. Ndithudi Satana amafesa chidani pakati pawo. Ndithudi Satana, kwa munthu, ndi mdani woonekeratu"
  17,54,Ambuye wanu amadziwa kwambiri za inu ndipo ngati Iye afuna adzakuchitirani chifundo kapena ngati Iye afuna adzakulangani. Ndipo Ife sitidakutumize iwe kuti ukhale wowayang’anira iwo ayi
  17,55,"Ambuye wako amadziwa kwambiri zonse zimene zili kumwamba ndi padziko lapansi ndipo, ndithudi, Ife tidalemekeza Aneneri ena kuposa anzawo ndipo kwa Davide, Ife tidamupatsa Buku la Masalimo"
  17,56,"Nena, “Aitaneni onse amene mumadzinyengeza nawo mowonjezera pa Iye. Iwo alibe mphamvu zochotsa mavuto anu kapena kuwasintha ndi kupatsa munthu wina.”"
  17,57,"Iwo amene amawapembedza nawonso amafunafuna njira yodziyandikiritsira kwa Ambuye wawo, kuti ndani amene angakhale pafupi kwambiri ndi Mulungu ndipo amafunafuna mtendere wa Mulungu ndikuopa chilango chake. Ndithudi chilango cha Ambuye wako ndi chofuna kuopedwa"
  17,58,Ndipo palibe mzinda umene Ife sitingauononge kapena kuulanga ndi chilango choopsa tsiku lachiweruzo lisanadze. Izi zidalembedwa m’Buku
  17,59,"Ndipo palibe chimene chimatiletsa Ife kutumiza zizindikiro kupatula kuti anthu a mvula zakale sadazikhulupirire izo. Ndipo kwa anthu a Thamoud, Ife tidawapatsa ngamira yaikazi kukhala chizindikiro chooneka ndi maso komabe iwo adaichitira zoipa. Ndipo Ife sititumiza zizindikiro kupatula ndi cholinga chofuna kuchenjeza ndi kuwachititsa mantha"
  17,60,"Ndipo pamene tidakuuza kuti, “Ndithudi! Ambuye wako wawazungulira anthu. Ndipo Ife sitidapange masomphenya amene tidakuonetsa iwe koma kukhala mayeso kwa anthu chimodzimodzinso mtengo wotembereredwa umene watchulidwa m’Korani. Ife timawachenjeza ndi kuwachititsa mantha koma sizili kuwathandiza koma kuonjezera kusakhulupirira.”"
  17,61,"Ndipo pamene ife tidawauza angelo kuti, “Mugwadireni Adamu.” Onse adamugwadira iye kupatula Satana. Iye adayankha kuti, “Kodi ine ndimugwadire iye amene Inu mudamupanga kuchokera ku dothi?”"
  17,62,"Iye adati, “Mukumuona! Uyu ndiye amene mwamulemekeza kuposa ine ndipo ngati inu mundisunga ndi moyo mpaka patsiku louka kwa akufa, ine ndidzawasokoneza ana ake kupatula ochepa.”"
  17,63,"Mulungu adati, “Pita, ndipo aliyense wa iwo amene adzakutsatira, ndithudi, Gahena ndiyo idzakhala malipiro ake ndipo ndi malipiro okwana.”"
  17,64,"“Ndipo anyengerere amene ungawathe mwa iwo ndi mawu ako, ndipo menyana nawo ndi asirikali ako okwera akavalo ndi oyenda pansi, ndipo gawana nawo chuma ndi ana ndipo alonjeze.” Koma Satana sawalonjeza china chilichonse koma chinyengo"
  17,65,"“Ndithudi pa akapolo anga angwiro, iwe siudzakhala ndi mphamvu ina iliyonse pa iwo yowasokoneza. Ambuye wako ndi wokwana kukhala Mtetezi.”"
  17,66,Ambuye wanu ndiye amene amayendetsa zombo pa nyanja kuti mufunefune zokoma zake. Ndithudi Iye ali wachisoni ndi inu
  17,67,"Ndipo akakupezani mavuto pamene mulipanyanja, iwoamenemumawapembedzamowonjezera pa Iye amakuthawirani kupatula Iye yekha. Koma ngati Iye akupulumutsani kufika pa mtunda, mumatembenuka. Ndithudi, munthu ndi wamwano"
  17,68,Kodi inu muli ndi chikhulupiriro chakuti Iye sangakumizeni m’dera lililonse la pamtunda kapena kuti sangakutumizireni mphepo yamkuntho? Pamenepo inu simudzapeza wina aliyense wokuthandizani
  17,69,"Kapena inu mukukhulupirira kuti sangakubwezereninso m’nyanjamo kachiwiri ndi kukutumizirani mphepo yamkuntho, ndikukumizani chifukwa chakusakhulupirira kwanu ndipo kuti inu simudzapeza wokuthandizani polimbana ndi Ife"
  17,70,"Ndithudi Ife tawalemekeza ana a Adamu, ndipo Ife tawanyamula pamtunda ndi pa nyanja ndipo tawapatsa zinthu zabwino ndiponso tawalemekeza kuposa zina zimene talenga ndi ulemu wapadera"
  17,71,Ndipo kumbukira tsiku limene tidzaitana mtundu uliwonse wa anthu pamodzi ndi Atsogoleri awo. Ndipo yemwe adzapatsidwa Buku lake ku dzanja lamanja iwo adzawerenga Bukulo mwa chisangalalo ndipo sadzaponderezedwa ngakhale ndi pang’onong’ono pomwe
  17,72,Koma iye amene ali wakhungu m’moyo uno adzakhalanso wakhungu m’moyo umene uli nkudza ndipo adzasochera kwambiri
  17,73,Ndithudi iwo adali pafupi kuti akusokoneze ku zimene takuvumbulutsira iwe kuti utinamizire zina ndipo zikadatero akadakupala ubwenzi
  17,74,"Ngati Ife tikadapanda kulimbikitsa chikhulupiriro chako, padatsala pang’ono kuti uwatsatire"
  17,75,Ndipo zikadatero Ife tikadakulawitsa chilango chachikulu m’moyo uno ndi chilango chachikulu m’moyo umene uli nkudza. Kotero siukadapeza wina aliyense wokuthandiza ku mkwiyo wathu
  17,76,"Ndithudi adatsala pang’ono kukuchititsa mantha m’dziko ndi cholinga choti akuchotse m’menemo. Zikadatheka kutero iwo sakadakhala pambuyo pako, koma kwa kanthawi kochepa"
  17,77,Umenewu ndiwo mwambo wa Atumwi amene tidatumiza iwe usanadze ndipo iwe siudzapeza kusintha kulikonse m’mwambo wathu
  17,78,Chita mapemphero kuyambira nthawi yopendekera dzuwakufikirausikundipowerenga Koranim’mapemphero a m’mbandakucha. Ndithudi kuwerenga Korani nthawi ya m’mbandakucha kumachitilidwa umboni
  17,79,"Ndipo m’kati mwa usiku, pemphera ndi kuwerenga Korani ndi mapemphero oonjezera kwa iwe. Mwina Ambuye wako angadzakuike pamalo wotamandika"
  17,80,"Nena, “Ambuye ndilowetseni kulowa kwa bwino ndipo nditulutseni mwaubwino. Ndipo ndipatseni kuchokera kwa Inu mphamvu yondithandiza.”"
  17,81,"Nena, “Choonadi chadza ndipo bodza latha. Ndithudi bodza liyenera kutha.”"
  17,82,"Ndipo titumiza kuchokera m’Korani mankhwala ochiza ndiponso chisoni kwa onse okhulupirira, ndipo imaonjezera kwa anthu osakhulupirira chionongeko"
  17,83,"Ndipo tikam’patsa munthu zokoma zathu, iye amatembenuka ndi kuchita mwano ndipo amakhala kutali ndi njira yoyenera. Ndipo zikam’peza zoipa amakhala wotaya mtima kwambiri"
  17,84,"Nena, “Munthu aliyense amachita molingana ndi chikhalidwe chake koma Ambuye wanu amadziwa yemwe watsogozedwa bwino panjira yachilungamo.”"
  17,85,"IwoakukufunsazaMzimu.Ndiponena,“Ambuyewanga ndiye amene adziwa za iwo. Ndipo inu simudapatsidwe nzeru koma pang’ono pokha.”"
  17,86,"Ndithudi Ife tikadafuna, tikadakulanda chimene tavumbulutsa kwa iwe ndipo iwe siukadapeza wina aliyense wokuteteza kwa Ife m’malo mwako"
  17,87,"Kupatula chifundo chochokera kwa Ambuye wako, ndithudi ubwino wake pa iwe ndi waukulu zedi"
  17,88,"Nena, “Ngati anthu ndi majini akadagwirizana kubweretsa chofanana ndi Korani ino, iwo sakadabweretsa chofanana nayo ngakhale kuti iwo akadathandizana.”"
  17,89,Ndithudi talongosola kwa anthu mu Korani ino chitsanzo chilichonse. Komabe anthu ambiri akana choonadi ndi kukhala osakhulupirira
  17,90,"Iwo amati, “Ife sitidzakukhulupirira iwe mpaka pamene utatitumphutsira kasupe kuchokera pansi.”"
  17,91,“Kapena utakhala ndi munda wa tende ndi mphesa ndipo m’kati mwake utumphutse mitsinjeyaikulu.”
  17,92,“Kapenaugwetsemtambopaifemonga momwe udatilonjezera kapena utibweretsere Mulungu pamodzi ndi angelo pamaso pathu.”
  17,93,"“Kapena ukhale ndi nyumba yokongoletsedwa bwino kwambiri kapena ukwere kumwamba. Komabe ife sitidzakukhulupirira kukwera kwako mpaka pamene utatitsitsira ife Buku kuti tiziwerenga.” Nena, “Alemekezeke Ambuye wanga! Ndithudi ine sindine aliyense koma munthu amene watumizidwa ngati Mtumwi.”"
  17,94,"Ndipo palibe chimene chidawaletsa anthu kukhala okhulupirira pamene malangizo adadza kwa iwo koma mwano chifukwa iwo amati, “Kodi Mulungu watumiza munthu kukhala Mtumwi?”"
  17,95,"Nena, “Ngati angelo akadakhala pa dziko lapansi, namayenda mwamtendere, ndithudi, Ife tikadatumiza kwa iwo mngelo kuchoka kumwamba ngati Mtumwi.”"
  17,96,"Nena, “Mulungu ndi wokwana kukhala mboni pakati pa ine ndi inu. Ndithudi! Iye ndi wodziwa ndi woona zonse za akapolo ake.”"
  17,97,"Ndipo aliyense amene Mulungu wamutsogolera , atsogozedwa bwino koma iye amene Iye amusocheza wotere iwe siungamupezere mtetezi wina aliyense kupatula Iye yekha. Ndipo Ife tidzawasonkhanitsa onse pa tsiku la kuuka kwa akufa, akuyenda pa nkhope zawo, akhungu, abububu ndi agonthi, malo awo adzakhala Gahena ndipo pamene malawi ake azikazima tizidzawaonjezera moto"
  17,98,"Amenewo ndiwo malipiro awo chifukwa iwo sadakhulupirire mawu athu ndipo adati, “Pamene ife tidzasanduka mafupa ndi kufufutika, kodi tidzaukitsidwa kukhala chilengedwe chatsopano?”"
  17,99,Kodi iwo saona kuti Mulungu amene adalenga kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi ali ndi mphamvu yolenga zofanana ndi iwo? Ndipo Iye adawaikira iwo nthawi yosakayikitsa. Komabe anthu ochimwa amakana choonadi ndikusankha kusakhulupirira
  17,100,"Nena, “Ngati mukadakhala ndi nkhokwe za chifundo cha Ambuye wanga, ndithudi, inu mukanazibisa poopa kuti zingathe.” Ndithudi munthu ndi waumbombo"
  17,101,"Ndithudi Ife tidamupatsa Mose zizindikiro zisanu ndi zinayi zooneka. Afunse ana a Israyeli pamene iye adadza kwa iwo ndipo Farawo adati kwa iye, “Iwe Mose, ndithudi, ine ndili kukuganizira kuti ndiwe wolodzedwa.”"
  17,102,"Iye adati, “Ndithudi iwe uli kudziwa bwinobwino kuti zizindikiro izi sizinatumizidwe ndi wina koma Ambuye wakumwamba ndi dziko lapansi ngati umboni wooneka ndi maso. Ndipo, ndithudi, ine ndiganiza kuti iwe, Farawo, ndiwe woonongeka.”"
  17,103,Farawo anafunitsitsa kuti awapirikitse m’dziko. Koma Ife tidamumiza pamodzi ndi onse amene adali naye
  17,104,"Ndipo pambuyo pake Ife tidati kwa ana a Israyeli, “Khalani m’dziko ndipo pamene lonjezo lomaliza lidzadza, Ife tidzakusonkhanitsani kukhala malo amodzi.”"
  17,105,Ifetavumbulutsa Bukula Koranim’choonadindipondi m’choonadi latsika. Ndipo Ife takutumiza iwe osati wina kuti ukalalikire nkhani za bwino ndi kupereka chenjezo
  17,106,Ndi Buku la Korani limene tagawa m’zigawo kuti iwe uwerenge kwa anthu mwakanthawi. Ife talivumbulutsa pang’onopang’ono
  17,107,"Nena, “Zili kwa inu kulikhulupirira kapena kusalikhulupirira. Ndithudi! Iwo amene adapatsidwa nzeru ilo lisadadze, likamawerengedwa kwa iwo, amagwetsa mphumi zawo pansi.”"
  17,108,"Ndipo iwo amati, “Ulemerero ndi wa Ambuye wathu! Ndithudi lonjezo la Ambuye wathu likwaniritsidwe.”"
  17,109,"Ndipo iwo amagwa pansi pa zipumi zawo, ali kulira ndipo limawaonjezera kudzichepetsa"
  17,110,"Nena, “Muitaneni Mulungu kapena Mwini chifundo chosatha, m’dzina lililonse limene mungamuitanire, chifukwa Iye ali ndi mayina abwino. Ndipo musanene mapemphero anu mokweza kapena motsitsa koma sankhani mawu a pakati ndi pakati.”"
  17,111,"Nena, “Kuyamikidwa konse ndi kwa Mulungu, amene sanabale mwana wamwamuna ndipo alibe mnzake womuthandiza mu Ufumu wake, ndipo Iye siwopanda mphamvu kuti angakhale ndi womuthandiza. Motero mulemekezeni Iye ndi ulemu woyenera Iye yekha.”"